data.description: We are pleased to announce an INCREDIBLE DUPLEX OPPORTUNITY PRICED TO SELL, in THE HEART OF Boyle Heights, prime location near bars, coffee shops, and museums and minutes away from Downtown LA, an 8-minute walk to the LAC * USC Medical Center, quick access to the 10, 5 and 101 Fwys. One of the units is beautifully remodeled, and the second unit needs TLC. The garage is DETACHED & perfect for a STUDIO conversion. Both units have individual gas and electrical meters and are TENANT OCCUPIED, Property will be SOLD with current tenants. SELLER IS MOTIVATED!!  Put your thinking caps to prevent missing out on this great future investment opportunity! Call for more details.
